# Digital Banking Cybersecurity Checklist

## Purpose
This checklist helps banks, fintechs, IT auditors, cybersecurity teams, and compliance professionals assess cybersecurity controls for digital banking platforms, including internet banking, mobile banking, API banking, payment services, and customer-facing financial applications.

## Scope
This checklist may be used for:
- Internet banking platforms
- Mobile banking applications
- Open banking/API platforms
- Payment gateways
- Customer portals
- Agent banking platforms
- Digital onboarding systems
- Card and transaction services
- Third-party fintech integrations

