## Risk Rating Guide

| Rating | Description |
|---|---|
| Critical | Immediate risk to customer funds, sensitive data, regulatory compliance, or service availability |
| High | Significant control weakness requiring urgent remediation |
| Medium | Moderate risk requiring planned remediation |
| Low | Minor weakness or improvement opportunity |

